
iptables -t nat -A PREROUTING -i vmbr0 -p ####(Network Protocol) --dport ####(Port) -j DNAT --to-destination 10.0.0.1(VM/CT-IPv4):####(Port)

For Example: iptables -t nat -A PREROUTING -i vmbr0 -p tcp --dport 221 -j DNAT --to-destination 10.0.0.1:22
- ssh user@public_ip -p 221 - to ssh directly into the vm/ct. - make sure you execute the rc.local file and that it has the permission it needs.